high_descs: Turn left, go to and face the wall.
Take the candle on the corner of the tub to the right.
Turn around, go straight, turn right, go straight, turn left, go in between the dresser and the toilet and face the dresser.
But the candle on the bottom shelf of the dresser near the edge.
Turn left,  go straight, turn right, go to the right side of the tub. Face the wall to the right.
Take the candle from the corner of the tub to the left.
Turn right, go straight, turn left, go in between the dresser and the toilet and face the dresser.
But the candle on the bottom shelf of the dresser to the right of the other candle.
anns.task_desc: Put candles on the shelf of a dresser.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the wall.
Pick up the candle on the end of the bathtub.
Go across the room to the toilet and turn left to face the shelf.
Set the candle down on the bottom shelf.
Turn left and walk to the center of the room and hang a right to the bathtub.
Turn right and pick up the candle on the end of the bathtub.
Turn right, walk to the center of the room and turn left between the shelf and toilet.
Turn left to face the cabinet and place the candle on the bottom shelf.
anns.task_desc: Move both candles from the bathtub to the shelf.

high_descs: Turn left and move to the beige hanging towel on the wall.
Pick up the candlestick on the corner of the bathtub closest to the towel.
Turn around and move to the other end of the bathtub then turn right and move to the cabinet facing the toilet.
Place the candlestick on the shelf above the top drawer of the cabinet.
Turn left, move towards the sink, then turn right and move to the end of the bathtub facing the drain.
Pick up the candlestick on the edge of the bathtub next to the wall and to the right of the shower handle.
Turn to the right, move past the sink, then turn left and face the cabinet.
Place the candlestick on the cabinet shelf to the right of the candlestick already placed there.
anns.task_desc: Place two candlesticks on a cabinet shelf.
